text: Rosa María Flores Buendía is a Mexican pelotari. She competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics. and 2019 Pan American Games. During the 1990 Basque Pelota World Championship, the 1994 Basque Pelota World Championship and the 1998 Basque Pelota World Championship she won the gold medal in the frontenis specialty with Miryam Muñoz Cadena. In the Basque Pelota World Championship of 2006, she won the bronze medal with Ariana Yolanda Cepeda de la Mora. == References == Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:Olympians for Mexico
